<title>RA TUAH, RA TUAH, EMMANUEL CH80</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ra tuah, ra tuah, Emmanuel, Israel thongtla run tlan hna, Ngaihchiat
 lunghno an tah lio ah, Pathian Fapa a rat hlan tiang.

[C1]
   Lawm tuah! Lawm tuah! Emmanuel, A ra than lai, Maw Israel.

[V2]
 Ra tuah, ra tuah, Nang Je-si-nge, Satan kut in na mi luatter, Hell
 chungin na mi khamh tuah hna, Thihnak ralteinak run pe hna.

[C2]
   Lawm tuah! Lawm tuah! Emmanuel, A ra than lai, Maw Israel.

[V3]
 Ra tuah, Ceunak, Bawi kan lungthin, Na rat thawngin lawmhter ko tuah,
 Muihnak kha run ceuter ko tuah, Khuadawm tianter law ceu kan pe.

[C3]
   Lawm tuah! Lawm tuah! Emmanuel, A ra than lai, Maw Israel.

[V4]
 Ra tuah David Fa, Kan Bawipa, Vancung innka kan hunpiak tuah, Vancung
 ram ah kan huhphenh tuah, Lam har kha kan khampiak ko sawh, Lawm tuah!
 Lawm tuah! Emmanuel a ra than lai, Maw Israel.

[C4]
   Lawm tuah! Lawm tuah! Emmanuel, A ra than lai, Maw Israel.</lyrics>
<key>E</key>
</song>